b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2526,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding an Issue with the Adventurer Gala Luca\'s Shared Skill Shining Slash [update]","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1636684200\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>Items were sent as gestures of goodwill around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1636684200\\"><\/span>. Affected players can claim these items from their goodie boxes.<br><br>Thank you for your understanding.<\/div><hr><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634092200\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>We have confirmed that this issue affects the adventurer Gala Notte as well.<br><br>\\u25bcIssue Details<br>https:\/\/dragalialost.com\/en\/news\/detail\/2234<br><br>We are planning to address this issue at a later date and will send the six light tomes required to unlock the Shining Slash shared skill to players who unlocked it after obtaining Gala Notte following the release of version 2.8.0 and before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634092200\\"><\/span>.<\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div>We have confirmed the occurrence of the following issue.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Issue Details<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhen used as a shared skill, the effects of the adventurer Gala Luca&#39;s skill Shining Slash apply to the skills used by the adventurers Joker, Mona, Panther, and Sophie while their Personas are summoned, and to the adventurer Gala Zethia while Bahamut is summoned.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We are planning to address this issue at a later date and will send the six light tomes required to unlock the Shining Slash shared skill to players who unlocked it after obtaining one or more of the affected adventurers and before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1632981600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1632981600,"prev_article_id":"2604","next_article_id":"2580","image_path":"","update_time":1636684498}}}'